NOTE on optional dependencies: this project's own code is MIT-licensed. The
OPTIONAL `[browser]` extra pulls in `nodriver` (AGPL-3.0); it is not required
for the core/free OA path and is only used if you explicitly opt into route-B
browser capture. Installing/using that optional dependency subjects that usage
to AGPL-3.0 terms. All other runtime paths depend only on permissively-licensed
packages (e.g. `requests`).
